HEADWORD: Gunter rig
<hw>Gun"ter rig`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>A topmast
arranged with metal bands so that it will readily slide up and down the
lower mast.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

